-- Nokia Siemens to buy Motorola assets for $1.2 billion
-- 
-- Mon Jul 19, 2010 7:23am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/07/19/us-nokia-motorola-idUSTRE66I23F20100719

 

 HELSINKI  (Reuters) - Nokia Siemens ( SIEGn.DE ) NSN.UL says it will buy Motorola's wireless network infrastructure assets in a deal valued at $1.2 billion. Nokia Siemens expects deal to close at the end of 2010. 

